         <abstract>
            <p>This article presents a simple methodology that can be used to increase productivity and reduce ergonomic risk in the workplace environment. First, the procedure will be presented and discussed in a step-by-step format. This ergonomic process will be applied and presented as an example from the aviation maintenance workplace.</p>
